reviewText: This tape had way too much cardio for the average housewife.  I only used it one time & now it sits.

This video was everything I had remembered.  Was sad when my copy was damaged a few years ago.  Lots and lots (and lots) of plyometrics!  Great cardio routine in the typical Firm fashion.  Love the set and the music.  Love that the instructors call muscle groups by name instead of using words like "tummy" or "fanny".  These workouts use great science to achieve maximum fitness.  RIP Anna Benson, you were ahead of your time!
